	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/cmplx.cuh: Add device functions to compute
	  complex unary functions.  Placed device functions in 'dev' namespace
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/exp.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/recip.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/mag.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/vdiv.cu: Use device functions from 'dev'
	  namespace.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/magsq.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/arg.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/euler.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/ceil.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/convnd2d.cu: Use device functions from 'dev'
	  namespace.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/corrnd2d.cu: Use device functions from 'dev'
	  namespace.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/reductions.cu: Use device functions from 'dev'
	  namespace.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/floor.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/log10.cu: Use device functions from 'dev'
	  namespace.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/tan.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/sq.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/real.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/conj.cu New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/tanh.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/asin.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/cosh.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/exp10.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/sinh.cu: New CUDA kernel for unary function
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/conv.cu: Use device functions from 'dev'
	  namespace.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/unary.hpp: Added evaluators for new unary functions.

