2010-08-20  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/core/reductions/reductions.hpp: Implemented redimensioning 
	  of dense matrix and tensor views so they run as fast as vectors for 
	  backends that use direct data access.
	* src/vsip/opt/cbe/ppu/reductions.hpp: Fixed a signed/unsigned comparison
	  warning on the threshold comparison.
	* tests/reduction_performance.cpp: New test to verify the above.
	* tests/reductions.cpp: Test split into common header and two source files.
	* tests/reductions.hpp: Common definitions from above.
	* tests/reductions_fp.cpp: Floating point cases.
	* tests/reductions_int.cpp: Integer and boolean cases.

