2010-06-30  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/opt/simd/svmul.cpp: Added new instantiations.
	  (VSIP_IMPL_INLINE_LIBSIMD) Removed dead macro.
	* src/vsip/opt/simd/svmul.hpp: Removed inline variants as
	  dead code.  Added coverage for new cases now handled by
	  the evaluator (both optimized and non-optimized versions).
	* src/vsip/opt/simd/eval_generic.hpp: Removed restriction
	  that vectors had to be complex.  Added constraint that
	  mixed-precision expressions are not allowed.

