	  'sync' parameter.
	  (invalidate_host/invalidate_device): Make public instead of private.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/dda.hpp: Check sync policy in constructors where
	  internal storage is used and mark host buffer as 'invalid' for
	  cases where the policy is 'out'.  Add comments to clarify.

