2010-06-14  Brooks Moses  <brooks@codesourcery.com>

	Merged from 2.3:
	2010-05-21  Stefan Seefeld  <stefan@codesourcery.com>
	* GNUmakefile.in (install_acconfig): New function.
	* src/vsip/GNUmakefile.inc.in: Use it.
	* src/vsip/core/config.hpp: Remove obsolete #undef directives.

2010-06-14  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* m4/fft.m4: Add -mabi=altivec for all power platforms when building
	  FFTW libraries.

2010-06-13  Stefan Seefeld  <stefan@codesourcery.com>

	* tests/extdata_subviews_v.cpp: Remove obsolete plainblock.hpp header.
	* tests/extdata-runtime.cpp: Likewise.
	* tests/extdata_subviews_m.cpp: Likewise.
	* tests/extdata.cpp: Likewise.
	* tests/extdata-fft.cpp: Likewise.
	* tests/extdata-matadd.cpp: Likewise.

2010-06-11  Stefan Seefeld  <stefan@codesourcery.com>

	* examples/stencil.cpp: Move to...
	* examples/pi/stencil.cpp: ...here, and adjust.
	* examples/sobel.cpp: Move to...
	* examples/pi/sobel.cpp: ...here, and adjust.
	* examples/pi/makefile.standalone.in: New file.
	* examples/png.cpp: Move to...
	* examples/io/png.cpp: ...here.

2010-06-11  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/core/cvsip/fft.hpp: Include header for std::auto_ptr.

2010-06-11  Justin Voo  <justin@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/convnd.cu: Remove remaining global memory
	  reads for edge conditions.

2010-06-08  Justin Voo  <justin@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip_csl/plainblock.hpp: Remove as obsolete.
	* benchmarks/mcopy.cpp: Adjust.
	* benchmarks/prod.cpp: Adjust.
	* benchmarks/ipp/mcopy.cpp: Adjust.
	* tests/view_lvalue.cpp: Adjust.
	* tests/regressions/proxy_lvalue_conv.cpp: Adjust.

2010-06-08  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/opt/simd/eval_generic.hpp: Fix error in checking result
	  type that was preventing binary expresssions from matching the
	  SIMD evaluator.

2010-06-07  Stefan Seefeld  <stefan@codesourcery.com>

        * src/vsip/opt/expr/assign_fwd.hpp: Give CUDA BE higher precedence.

2010-06-04  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* doc/reference-manual/fftm.xml: Document memory requirements for FFTs.
	* doc/reference-manual/fft.xml: Likewise.
	* doc/GNUmakefile.in: Added source dependencies for reference manual.

2010-06-01  Justin Voo  <justin@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/core/reductions/reductions.hpp: Added CUDA backend to list.
	* src/vsip/opt/reductions/reductions.hpp:  Added CUDA backend to list.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/reductions.cu: CUDA kernels for sum, sum of
	  squared values, and mean.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/reductions.hpp: Implementation of CUDA sum, sumsq, 
	  and mean functions.

2010-06-01  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/core/extdata.hpp (const_data): Added new member function 
	  that always returns a const pointer.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/matvec.hpp: Use const version above in the 
	  run-time valid checks.

