2010-05-29  Justin Voo <justin@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/corr.hpp: Added CUDA correlation functions.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/conv.cu: Modified CUDA convolution
	  kernels to function for correlation.
	* src/vsip/core/signal/corr.hpp: Added CUDA correlation to tag
	  list.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/cmplx.cuh: Added function for 
	  optional complex multiply with conjugation.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/conv.hpp: Modified CUDA convolution class
	  implementation to use modified CUDA convolution kernels.

2010-05-28  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/matvec.hpp(gemp, outer): Corrected errors in two
	  CUDA BLAS wrapper functions where the output is also an input.

2010-05-27  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/conv.hpp: Removed two unused variables.
	* tests/conv-2d.cpp: Disabled VERBOSE debug switch.

