	  generation option.
	* scripts/datasheet.db: Renamed from ds.db.  Removed missing 
	  benchmark cases (vthresh, lvgt, vsmss).
	* scripts/char.pl (-hpec): Support for new option.
	* scripts/hpec_datasheet.db: New file.  Datasheet for HPEC benchmark data.
	* scripts/ds.db: Renamed to datasheet.db.
	* scripts/makefile.hpec: New file.  Makefile for HPEC datasheet.
	* scripts/makefile.datasheet: Clean up.

