2010-05-12  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/core/matvec_prod.hpp: Added CUDA tag to prod type list
	  used by dispatch.
	* src/vsip/core/matvec.hpp: Added CUDA tag to gemp type list.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/matvec.hpp: Added matrix-vector, vector-matrix,
	  matrix-matrix and generalized matrix product evaluators.  Added
	  debug return value checks to CUBLAS calls.  Included a call to 
	  sync threads after calling gemm/v (based on empirical need).
	* benchmarks/mvprod.cpp: New file, benchmark matrix-vector products.
	* benchmarks/vmprod.cpp: New file, benchmark vector-matrix products.
	* benchmarks/mprod.hpp: New file, matrix product base class used in
	  above two files.

