	*  src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/vadd.cu: Add real + complex and complex + real functions
	and associated kernels.
	*  src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/vmul.cu: Add real * complex and complex * real functions
	and associated kernels.
	*  src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/vsub.cu: Add real - complex and complex - real functions
	and associated kernels.
	*  src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/vdiv.cu: Add real / complex and complex / real functions
	and associated kernels.

