2010-04-08  Brooks Moses  <brooks@codesourcery.com>

	* m4/lapack.m4: Revise link order for builtin-atlas
	  configuration and use ATLAS CBLAS bindings.
	  (USE_BUILTIN_BLAS): New configure variable.
	* vendor/GNUmakefile.inc.in (vendor_LIBF77): Rename to...
	  (vendor_CLAPACK_LIBF77) ...this, for clarity.
	  (lib/libblas.a): Move related targets to a new section
	  controlled by USE_BUILTIN_BLAS.
	* vendor/clapack/SRC/make.inc.in: Use USE_BUILTIN_BLAS,
	  not obsolete USE_SIMPLE_LAPACK, to control the usage of
	  -DNO_BLAS_WRAP.  Update comment to reflect current usage.

