	  (impl_data): Added missing member functions to 2-D block.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/eval_transpose.hpp (Block_helper): Added new
	  helper class to allow transpose to work with Gpu_block.  Use
	  it in exec() functions to obtain proper block type.  Changed
	  rt_valid() to use Ext_data instead of Device_memory to avoid
	  redundant copies.
