2009-07-01  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/bindings.hpp: Added new bindings for test kernels.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels.hpp: Added new kernels used for testing.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/util.hpp (Dev_props): New structure that
	  encodes parameters determined the "compute capability" of the device.
	  (distribute_matrix): New elementwise matrix distribution function.
	  (is_matrix_distributable): Determines if a matrix is too large to
	  be computed in a single kernel call.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/kernels/test.cu: New kernels for test that rely
	  on the new distribution functions above.
	* tests/cuda/distrib.cpp: New tests for same.

