	  account for dimension ordering.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/device_memory.hpp (size, stride): New functions.

2009-06-12  Don McCoy  <don@codesourcery.com>

	* src/vsip/opt/fft/workspace.hpp: Corrected real cases to obtain
	  the stride from the block (as is done in the complex cases).
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/fft.cpp: Relaxed row-stride assertion
	  checks to allow valid cases where the stride is greater than
	  the row length.
	* src/vsip/opt/cuda/fft.hpp: Modified the size limits to accept
	  a minimum FFT length of two.

